# Fixes

## Fix the font

echo "Fix the font: "
echo "1. Open Settings -> Appearance."
echo "2. Select the Fonts tab."
echo "3. "Enable anti-aliasing" should be checked and "slight" should be selected in the "Hinting" menu."

## Fix the keymapping

echo "The ChromeOS buttons are still mostly mapped to the old function keys. Here's the fix:"

echo "1. Exit ubuntu and launch crosh by pressing [CTRL]+[ALT]+[T]"
echo "2. ChromeOS> shell"
echo "3. $ sudo sh -e ~/Downloads/crouton -r precise -t keyboard -u"
